Decision	Rationale
Mock API for demo	Real backend not needed. Focus on UX patterns, not infrastructure.
Shared types folder	Single source of truth. If CLI says rollout_percentage, Dashboard must too.
Exit codes for CLI	Machines depend on numeric codes. Humans read text output. Both served.
No authentication	Out of UX scope. Assume OAuth exists in real deployment.
LocalStorage persistence	Demo-only. Real app would use backend database.
