11.6 Design Philosophy Summary
The goal of this project is to demonstrate that developer tooling can have coherent, humane design across every surface it touches. The CLI serves engineers who type. The Dashboard serves product managers who configure. The SDK serves pipelines that automate. Different interactions, same mental model. Same colors. Same terminology. Same exit codes. The hard part isn't building one good interface — it's building three that feel like they came from the same mind.

